{"tid":1807492,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩佬睇對手戰術紙：我對白癡無禮","createTime":"2020-01-02T00:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T04:14:22.000Z","uid":78243,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f1142e0f991bb9e60c1bab5ddb287f185a9c12f6","tid":1807492,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T00:24:12.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】熱刺在周三英超作客以0:1敗予修咸頓，領隊摩連奴認為這場一場奇怪的比賽，就觀看人家戰術指而遭警告一事，他並沒抱怨。<br />\n<br />\n「這場比賽有點奇怪。我們防守沒有問題，他們也沒有製造出甚麼麻煩，但攻入了1球。」摩連奴（Jose Mourinho）認為修咸頓一對中堅表現出色，「兩人很進取，沒有犯錯，令我們的攻擊球員很難踢。」<br />\n<br />\n熱刺今場有中場當比利、射手哈利簡尼先後傷出，摩佬表示：「沒有簡尼及另一名前鋒，孫興敏又停賽，我們沒有太多選擇。簡尼之前踢足每一分鐘，傷患可能嚴重，可能輕微。」面對傷兵，摩連奴坦言增兵，但不會豪使，「我們不打算做轉會市場的王帝。」<br />\n<br />\n他在比賽期間因為走到修咸頓後備席「明睇」對方的戰術紙，被球證以黃牌警告，「我很無禮，我對白癡無禮，明顯地我值得拿黃牌。」據指，他當時是觀看對方守門員教練史柏克的戰術紙，並與人家發生言語衝突。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP<br />\n<br />\n摩狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692a0f0c36fa868d35a19c32c5d600bfabee5609","tid":1807492,"uid":1065,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T00:35:46.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;I think the yellow card is fair because I was rude, but I was rude to an idiot,&rdquo; said Mourinho. &ldquo;For some reason I was rude. But I was, and because I was rude I deserve the yellow card. Basically, I had bad words with the guy.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n搶口到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4956fc762b61f394ca4301afe09abe155a17d2fb","tid":1807492,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"692a0f0c36fa868d35a19c32c5d600bfabee5609","tid":1807492,"uid":1065,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T00:35:46.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;I think the yellow card is fair because I was rude, but I was rude to an idiot,&rdquo; said Mourinho. &ldquo;For some reason I was rude. But I was, and because I was rude I deserve the yellow card. Basically, I had bad words with the guy.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n搶口到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g